article_title: Welcome to day one of ‘Obamacare’ enrollment…now please wait.
article_text:
October 1, 2013 – Day one for people to enroll in Obamacare. The administration has had years to prepare for this day – YEARS.

As MSNBC’s Ed Schultz has instructed us, I visited the website to see what the sign-up process would be like. After entering my state and status as an individual, I was greeted by the following screen.

After several minutes of patience…this screen popped up.

This appears to qualify as a FAIL.

This is probably just a small computer problem. It’s doubtful there will be any issues or delays when you actually try to get treatment from a doctor.
